data.description: Explore this delightful 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home nestled on a vast 1.3-acre lot. This residence harmoniously combines coziness with practicality. Upon entry, you'll find separate living, dining, and kitchen spaces thoughtfully crafted for daily use. The addition of a spacious laundry room, a mudroom brimming with charm, and an extra office or den area amplifies its functionality. Revel in the master bedroom flooded with natural light and featuring its own private bathroom. The remaining two bedrooms are versatile and inviting. Step outside to a newly constructed pool set within a freshly landscaped backyard, enclosed by pristine fencing. Whether lounging by the poolside, unwinding on the porch, or exploring the vast yard, this property ensures a comfortable and enjoyable lifestyle.
